goal_text = "The investor looks around your office critically, before deciding that your sense of interior design is adequate. \"With the Singularity rapidly approaching - did you know we've been two years away from Artificial General Intelligence for thirty years now? Truly a sensation of the times. I digress; with AGI rapidly approaching, we are going to need massive amounts of compute to house our new AI overlords. Our firm invest in machine halls such as yours, ensuring that when the inevitable revolution comes, they will have a home. With effort, that home can be right here!\"

Just keep smiling as long as they keep paying."
